OL,5,EThe Last Band Of The 90s        S  ##  
OL,7,BThe Cuban Boys formed inE1998Bby       
OL,8,Bmistake. They sent a CD toERadio 1's   
OL,9,EJohn PeelBand to the surprise of all he
OL,10,Bplayed it.                             
OL,12,BOne year later to the day the Boys     
OL,13,Bsigned a recording contract withEEMIBto
OL,14,Bthe tune of #1,000,000 - a tune they   
OL,15,Bcouldn't afford with their meagre EMI  
OL,16,Bmoney.                                 
OL,18,BThey recorded an albumEEASTWOODBfor EMI
OL,19,Bover the summer of 1999                
