OL,5,EThe Last Band Of The 90s        S  ##  
OL,7,BIn December 1999 the lead single       
OL,8,ECognoscenti Vs IntelligentsiaBtook on  
OL,9,BCliff Richard and Westlife for the     
OL,10,BChristmas number 1.                    
OL,12,BIt did not succeed, and was also beaten
OL,13,BbyEJohn Lennon,Bwho was at the time    
OL,14,Bstill dead.                            
OL,16,EEMIBsoon dropped the band making their 
OL,17,B18 monthErise and fallBone of the most 
OL,18,Bspectacular in pop history.            
